snippet.textDisplay:
Bison go up to level 5. They make diamond at 5 and sometimes 4. 
If you want your best chances at spawning a diamond, do not go after the females. Killing them will not help you. Females will always respawn as females, which neve rmake diamond. 
For males, you only want to kill levels 3+! Doing this means the bison you left behind (level 2) will be very small. That will trick the game into spawning bigger animals to make up for the difference in level! 

Basic rules:
- Dont hunt females (unless theyre Gemsbok)
- If they go up to level 9, kill levels 5+ 
- If they go up to 5, kill 3+
- If they go up to 3, kill 2+ 

Happy hunting!
